### Test API Endpoints
### Bisa digunakan dengan REST Client extension di VSCode

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/

###
### POSTS ENDPOINTS
###

### Get all posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

### Get posts with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?page=1&limit=5&status=publish

### Get posts by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?category=berita

### Search posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts?search=teknologi

### Get popular posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/popular?limit=5

### Get recent posts
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/recent?limit=5

### Get single post by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/posts/contoh-artikel-pertama

### Create new post
POST {{baseUrl}}/posts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Artikel Test",
  "slug": "artikel-test",
  "content": "Ini adalah konten artikel test",
  "excerpt": "Excerpt artikel test",
  "status": "publish",
  "featured_image": "/uploads/images/test.jpg",
  "category_ids": [1, 2],
  "tag_ids": [1]
}

### Update post
PUT {{baseUrl}}/posts/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Artikel Test (Updated)",
  "status": "publish"
}

### Delete post
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/posts/1

###
### CATEGORIES ENDPOINTS
###

### Get all categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories

### Get single category
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/berita

### Get posts by category
GET {{baseUrl}}/categories/berita/posts?page=1&limit=10

### Create category
POST {{baseUrl}}/categories
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teknologi",
  "slug": "teknologi",
  "description": "Berita seputar teknologi"
}

### Update category
PUT {{baseUrl}}/categories/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Teknologi (Updated)"
}

### Delete category
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/categories/1

